Five girls show up in the middle of a Saturday wanting matching tattoos- Z and Charles helped us find the symbol we wanted, sized each one for us, since we all wanted it in different areas.
We were all in and out within an hour and treated very well.
The place was clean and the staff friendly.
Highly recommend!

