Made an appointment to get my first tattoo.
Tattoo artist Jason did an awesome job.
I provided the basic idea and let him design the rest.
Job took around 5 hours to complete.
Jason aka 'Bully' played music on the shops computer to help pass the time and keep my mind off the pain from the needle.
Wasn't sure what to expect since it was my first, but very pleased with the result.
See picture to see what I got done..it was a Randy Rhoads Jackson guitar impaled into my leg like an arrow.

